ed="T" n="0795a09"/><persName key="A010776">釋滿意</persName>，不知何許人也。風神峭拔，識量寬<lb
ed="T" n="0795a10"/>和，經論旁通，專於律學。<date notBefore-iso="+0624-08-17" key="j19492001949949" notAfter-iso="+0626-09-05"><name>武德</name>末</date>，所遇<placeName key="PL000000001481">鄴都</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0795a11"/><persName key="A000747">法礪<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，作疏<ptr target="#n903"/>解《曇無德律》<ptr target="#n70"/>，遂往摳衣，明<lb
ed="T" n="0795a12"/>其授受。如是講導三十許年。乃傳付<placeName key="PL000000042420">觀音寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0795a13"/><persName key="A010825">大亮<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>。<persName key="A010825">亮</persName>方授<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName><persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>。盛化之間，出龍<lb
ed="T" n="0795a14"/>象之資<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1172"/>，無過<persName key="A010776">意</persName>之門也矣<ptr target="#n929"/>。</p>
